### 1. 注册
POST http://localhost:8080/api/user/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testuser",
  "password": "123456"
}

### 2. 登录
POST http://localhost:8080/api/user/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testuser",
  "password": "123456"
}

### 3. 添加备忘录
POST http://localhost:8080/api/notes
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 1,
  "title": "今天的学习",
  "content": "完成了备忘录项目的开发"
}

### 4. 查所有备忘录（分页）
GET http://localhost:8080/api/notes/page?page=1&size=10

### 5. 查单个备忘录
GET http://localhost:8080/api/notes/1

### 6. 查某个用户的备忘录
GET http://localhost:8080/api/notes/user/1

### 7. 更新备忘录
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/notes/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "更新后的标题",
  "content": "更新后的内容"
}

### 8. 删除备忘录
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/notes/1

### 9. 🧪 参数校验：不传标题（应返回400）
POST http://localhost:8080/api/notes
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 1,
  "content": "没有标题的备忘录"
}

### 10. 🧪 参数校验：不传userId（应返回400）
POST http://localhost:8080/api/notes
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "没有用户ID",
  "content": "谁写的？"
}

### 11. 🧪 参数校验：啥都不传（应返回400）
POST http://localhost:8080/api/notes
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### 12. 🧪 重复注册用户名（应返回数据已存在）
POST http://localhost:8080/api/user/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testuser",
  "password": "123456"
}
